3 squares and an ed guardsmen sarah and jimmy inform double dee and eddy that ed has been grounded and the eds must stage a daring escape from the house without sarah and jimmy knowing 
 
dim lit ed after an encounter with jimmy jonny ed and eddy double dee has come to the conclusion that the whole cul-de-sac lacks good judgement he gets everyone together and encourages their education with a scavenger hunt this fails when the kids realize that the prize is not a jawbreaker which they at first came to believe 
