note in episode 310 “the one where rachel quits” set in december 1996 chandler says rachel is 28 and so she should turn 33 in this episode set in early 2001 moreover it is previously said elsewhere in seasons 4 and 5 that rachel was born on may 5th and not in the wintertime 
 
