a woman found in the park shows signs of being viciously assaulted she is identified as nafeesa amir the daughter of afghan diplomat saleh amir marshall manesh during the investigation the detectives learn that nafeesa and her brother jaleel anil kumar were raised according to taliban traditions in which an honor killing is the punishment for disobedience although her individually has been suppressed for her entire life the svu squad turns to aziza amir susham bedi for help hoping that the love she feels for her daughter is stronger 
 
