with the drought continuing and no money to buy feed or truck in water claire tess and nick join forces like the drovers of old they take their amalgamated herds out on the gungellan track meg is quietly delighted when the ryans send terry along to help and sees a chance to win him back from jane the attraction between nick and tess grows 
tess motivates claire into rekindling her dreams of becoming a stock horse trainer and breeder drovers run needs the money and with peter out of the way there is slim chance of crossing paths with him again theres no reason why the dream cant be pursued 
when a stranger knocks on their door in the middle of the night claiming a broken down van suspicions are aroused when it is discovered that the occupants of the van are strippers jodi is thriled and volunteers to cook them dinner with disastrous results 
everything from drovers is stolen as jodi and craig have a secret rendezvous in the spa when wilgul is also burgled tess and nick set a trap to catch the thieves 
