former cast member kevin nealon appears during weekend update to tell viewers that hes not on snl anymore and that viewers who do see him are watching reruns from the 1990s that at the time aired on comedy central 
winona ryder appears during the weekend update cliffhanger 
the special featured some of the best election material from this year and years past rachel dratch will ferrell and darrell hammond hosted the special while doing a number of different impressions this special also featured cameo appearances from george w bush al gore jesse ventura george hw bush barbara bush and dana carvey 
the culps mandatory drug awareness assembly sketch from this episode was included in the prime-time special snl mothers day special 2001 as well as the clip show the best of will ferrell 
the special featured some of the best material featuring molly shannon during her stint on the show sketches include mary katherine gallagher leg up the courtney love show pretty living delicious dish rockettes auditions monica lewinsky in congress fanatic film blind date at the airport veronica and co dame elizabeth taylor and jeannie darcy 
the first snl mothers day special since 1993 the episode featured the cast and their mothers talking about their favorite sketches aired on the show sketches included behind the music rock &amp roll heaven trl geminis twin mango vs jlo the weakest link and more this special contained a special tribute to singer-songwriter minnie riperton who was the mother of cast member maya rudolph 


 
