homer becomes a fortune cookie writer for a chinatown restaurant mr burns reads one of homers fortunes which says that the reader will find love before flag day is over burns goes searching for love and meets gloria a meter maid and asks her out gloria reluctantly agrees and burns recruits homer to help him look young and hip to his new girlfriend 
