g with monica andrew and tess he tells kelly that her father was a brave man and that while two people died that day one little boys life was saved -- the man who is being honored this evening as man of the year -- brandon white brandon white then steps up to the podium to deliver his acceptance speech he speaks of the perfect stranger kellys father who gave his life for his and explains how he dedicated himself to be deserving of the second chance he received guest star mel harris and joel grey 
